item.title: CVE-2023-3512|2024-08-02T06:55:03.662Z -- setelsa%20security -- conacwin%20cb
item.description: Relative path traversal vulnerability in Setelsa Security's ConacWin CB, in its 3.8.2.2 version and earlier, the exploitation of which could allow an attacker to perform an arbitrary download of files from the system via the "Download file" parameter.
